metadata.name: Quantum Key - LA
metadata.description:
Quantum Space LA is a 3800 sq ft community hub opening on the Santa Monica 3rd Street Promenade in June 2022.

The space features an NFT gallery and minting center with over 30 screens, a metaverse immersion room, artist-in-residence spaces, and an exclusive collectors' lounge open only to Quantum Key holders and their guests.
